  "text": "Probabilistic PCA is a special case of factor analysis under the assumption of isotropic noise [CITATION_1] . This restriction allows an analytic solution, which omits the EM-algorithm. The model density p(y, x) in joint space is described by a multivariate Gaussian, N (0, A −1 ) with",
